# fileLabels

**Instance Property**

The array of file labels, returned as strings.

## Declaration

```swift
var fileLabels: [String] { get }
```

## Return Value

An array of strings.

## Discussion

You can listen for notifications named [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSWorkspace/didChangeFileLabelsNotification] to be notified when file labels change.

You can safely call this method from any thread of your app.

## Finder File Labels

- **fileLabelColors**: The array of colors for the file labels.
